                  },
                  {
                      "line_number":  1132,
                      "text":  "I just didn\u0027t know.",
                      "start":  2736,
                      "label":  "fluff"
                  },
                  {
                      "line_number":  1134,
                      "text":  "I grew up with the Latino stepdad and he was great until, you know, occasionally we just",
                      "start":  2742,
                      "label":  "setup"
                  },
                  {
                      "line_number":  1135,
                      "text":  "dropped the N-bomb at Walmart, like out of nowhere.",
