                      "label":  "setup"
                  },
                  {
                      "line_number":  1139,
                      "text":  "\"Where\u0027d you fucking learn that word, dad?\"",
                      "start":  2753,
                      "label":  "setup"
                  },
                  {
                      "line_number":  1140,
                      "text":  "He goes, \"At work, well you shouldn\u0027t be using it.",
                      "start":  2755,
                      "label":  "setup"
                  },
                  {
                      "line_number":  1141,
                      "text":  "\"Unless we\u0027re at Home Depot",
